description: .NET Framework binding of RDKit Release_2021_03_1. Supports Windows (x86 and x64) and Linux (x64).
releaseNotes: This release uses Boost 1_74_0, Eigen 3.3.8, FreeType 2.10.4, zlib 1.2.11, libpng 1.6.37, pixman 0.40.0, cairo 1.16.0 built usng Visual Studio 16.0 for Windows.
title: RDKit C# Binding
